outputs.output_descr:
Project outputs:
- Enhanced capacity of the State Agency on State Financial Control and Fight against Corruption;
- Clear guidelines on budgetary issues developed and people are more aware on state budget, its resources, development and expenditures;
- Public awareness on corruption and its consequences improved and stigmatization of corruption increased.

Project outputs:
- Transparency and Accountability: Assessments and trainings for increasing transparency and accountability of the system of governance and the Security Sector;
- Human Rights: Capacity building for system of   internal control and accountability within the Public Sector  and promotioion of Effective Public Complaint Mechanism (PCM);
- Judicial reform: Promote newly adopted Criminal Procedures Code and assist Juvenile Justice.
